## Brand Equity Measurement Workflow

- [ ] 1. Define equity dimensions: Awareness, Associations, Perceived quality, Loyalty
- [ ] 2. Select metrics: Choose measurable KPIs for each dimension
- [ ] 3. Gather data: Pull from surveys, social listening, sales data, search data
- [ ] 4. Benchmark: Compare against competitors and previous periods
- [ ] 5. Diagnose: Identify what's driving or hurting equity
- [ ] 6. Recommend: Actionable steps to improve brand equity

## Key Inputs
- Brand: {{brand_name}}
- Competitors: {{competitors}}
- Time period: {{time_period}}
- Data sources: {{data_sources}}
